{"tid":2399340,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"平等機會性傾向資助計劃今日起接受申請","createTime":"2021-02-08T04:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T05:46:14.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46e83dcd6f0c01554d62cd5f841be8fbf687eaf1","tid":2399340,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局表示，今日開始接受2021/22年度平等機會（性傾向）資助計劃的申請。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，政府一直致力建立共融、互相尊重和不歧視的文化和價值觀，促進不同性傾向和跨性別人士的平等機會。有關計劃資助各項有意義的社區活動，藉以促進不同性傾向人士及跨性別人士享有平等機會，或為性小眾提供支援服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574710-20210208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574710-20210208.htm&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUijH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=2fe66588\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574710-20210208.htm&h=d21e71fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574710-20210208.htm</a>"},{"pid":"146effedf1f4856aea171cca9c0e17e6ec710dd4","tid":2399340,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"男兒身 女性格但TB ，易服癖偏男性化但同性戀中意女人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fef5bb22a43cf5f9946084df45063224389f59a","tid":2399340,"uid":58168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T05:46:14.000Z","msg":"我返工紮頭髮比人話可唔可以投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n（男，not gay）"}]}